            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I've been wondering about something for a while..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Do all cityfolk wear fashionable clothes like you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Am I really that fashionable?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes. You're so pretty, you're like a fairy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, thanks, but I'm more along the plain side..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "There are a looot of people who are prettier than me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see... When I grow up, I wanna wear frilly clothes, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "What you're wearing underneath is pretty, too. It's embroidered..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I guess cityfolk dress up, even in the places you don't see!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "What!? Tanya, where are you looking? Don't look there!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why not? They're so pretty."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure anyone you show them to will tell you they're beautiful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x39,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Whaaa... I don't need that kind<CR>of attention! Hrgh, this is so<CR>embarrassing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "When I make it out to the city, I wanna be as fashionable as you are, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x39,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Hyaaah, stop..."
        }
    ]
}